title: Toby Carvery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain of pub/restaurants - be warned that it's a carvery and is primarily meatstuff, but it's an option to go with non-veg diners. At lunch you will find around 4 vegetarian dishes, of which maybe 2 are vegan suitable. Could also order a few sides to make a meal, like roast potatoes, stuffing, apple sauce, etc. Ask about butter use. Gets busy at mealtimes.
